  <summary date="2018-02-15T05:00:00Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Opioid Response Enhancement Act

This bill amends the 21st Century Cures Act to reauthorize through FY2023 a program of grants to states and tribal entities to carry out activities addressing the opioid epidemic. It allows states and tribal entities to use the&#160;grants to carry out public health-related activities addressing other substance abuse that is a substantial or similar public health threat to the opioid epidemic.</summary>
